cy, reduces unsafe exploration in fragile systems, and enables zero-shot generalization to new environments by transferring meta-learned expectations about environmental passivity. We ground this in principles from causal discovery, algorithmic information theory, and fast adaptation, offering a scalable path toward AI systems that respect autonomy—whether in ecosystems, social systems, or human institutions—by defaulting to observation over intervention.",
